public class WeatherApp {
    private boolean isRainy;
    private int temperature;

    public WeatherApp(boolean isRainy, int temperature) {
        this.isRainy = isRainy;
        this.temperature = temperature;
    }

    public String getWeatherStatus() {
        if (isRainy) {
            return temperature < 15 ? "Cold and rainy" : "Mild and rainy";
        } else {
            return temperature >= 25 ? "Hot and sunny" : "Pleasant";
        }
    }

    public void updateWeather(boolean rain, int temp) {
        isRainy = rain;
        temperature = temp;
    }
}",

If 'Pleasant' is returned by getWeatherStatus, could this be because someone invoked updateWeather with isRainy set to false?
